<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.5.2">
<l>kalaiyāḷā vakalalkul kaṉavaḷaiyuṅ kaiyāḷā veṉcey kēṉnāṉ</l>
<l>vilaiyāḷā vaṭiyēṉai vēṇṭutiyō vēṇṭāyō veṉṉum meyya</l>
<l>malaiyāḷaṉ vāṉavartan talaiyāḷaṉ marāmaramē ḻeyta veṉṟic</l>
<l>cilaiyāḷa ṉeṉmakaḷaic ceytaṉaka ḷeṅṅaṉamnāṉ cintik kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Her] broad hips do not govern her girdle;</l>
<l rend="indent">[her] arms do not govern [her] gold bangles, either.</l>
<l>What do I do? She says, “Do you want me, [your] devotee who is a slave,</l>
<l rend="indent">or do you not?”</l>
<l>He of Meyya Mountain, ruler of the celestials, bearer victorious bow</l>
<l>Who shot seven pipal trees, how do I [even] think</l>
<l rend="indent">of what he did to my daughter?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
